- I've never changed one thing
about this room.

16:07.096 --> 16:09.533
Helps me remember Haley
as she was,

16:09.577 --> 16:12.145
not as a murder victim.

16:12.188 --> 16:14.190
- We're sorry if this brings up

16:14.234 --> 16:16.062
any painful memories,
Mrs. West.

16:16.105 --> 16:19.326
- They've never gone away.
