16:34.254 --> 16:36.038
helped her
with college planning.

16:36.082 --> 16:37.909
- So they spent
a lot of time together?

16:40.564 --> 16:43.524
- Is this about
that writer and his podcast?

16:43.567 --> 16:47.049
I told him I'd never let
my daughter's death

16:47.093 --> 16:49.747
be entertainment someone
