the time or the place.

28:58.649 --> 29:00.651
- Upset me?
You raped me.

29:00.695 --> 29:02.523
<i>♪</i>

29:02.566 --> 29:04.525
I want him arrested.

29:12.228 --> 29:14.317
- Is she okay?
Did you talk her down?

29:14.361 --> 29:15.928
- No, Burton,
I didn't talk her down.

29:15.971 --> 29:18.321
I listened to her.

29:18.365 --> 29:20.149
Fin and Rollins
are taking her to the station

29:20.193 --> 29:21.672
to get her statement.

29:21.716 --> 29:25.154
- Olivia, I swear to God,
I did not rape her.

29:25.198 --> 29:27.461
- Well, that's not
Andrea's recollection.

29:27.504 --> 29:30.420
- I haven't seen her
in 10 years.

29:30.464 --> 29:33.554
I am completely blindsided
by this.

29:35.730 --> 29:38.994
So you're saying that you two
were never involved.

29:39.038 --> 29:42.693
- I'm not saying that.
- Burton, so what did happen?

29:42.737 --> 29:44.347
- We had a flirtation

29:44.391 --> 29:46.088
the summer she worked
for my editor.

29:46.132 --> 29:48.351
The night before
she went back to college,

29:48.395 --> 29:51.877
I took her out for dinner
to say thanks.

29:51.920 --> 29:54.183
We had a few drinks.

29:54.227 --> 29:56.533
We ended up back
at my hotel room.

29:56.577 --> 29:59.362
It was completely consensual.
- And after?

29:59.406 --> 30:01.016
- She left later that night.

30:01.060 --> 30:03.845
I gave her the cab fare home.

30:03.889 --> 30:06.239
She never said a word.

30:08.415 --> 30:11.244
I have never been
in this situation before.

30:12.506 --> 30:16.292
Just tell me.
What do we do now?

30:16.336 --> 30:19.818
- We don't do anything.

30:19.861 --> 30:23.604
I have to recuse myself
from the case.

30:23.647 --> 30:27.129
My sergeant will call you
and let you know next steps.

30:30.306 --> 30:32.874
- Understood.

30:35.921 --> 30:39.402
<i>♪</i>

30:39.446 --> 30:40.926
- It was the night
before I left

30:40.969 --> 30:43.058
for my senior year at Holyoke.

30:43.102 --> 30:44.581
I tried to put it
out of my mind.

30:44.625 --> 30:47.062
I managed to do that
